<A>__{the truck speeds past forrest as he turns from the road and runs onto the high school football field. forrest runs across the field during a football scrimmage. in the stands watching the scrimmage is the legendary university of alabama football coach bear bryant, wearing his trademark plaid hat. a group of assistant coaches sit around him, as well as the high school football coach. the quarterback throws the ball into the air. forrest runs past the quarterback. the receiver catches the ball. forrest runs past the receiver as an opposing player tackles the stunned receiver. the football coach stands, followed by the assistant coaches.}
